      "writtenOn": "2020-12-15T17:21:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So the problem is that we share skia\u0027s gen_tasks_logic with a couple of other repos which may want CAS inputs from multiple top-level directories, so we can\u0027t assume we\u0027re sitting in the correct directory.",
